				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Note, also, that the hotkey need only be pressed once and the HoTT window stays up until you are no longer grouped or no longer in a group (or raid) with a leader who has that AA.
<br />

<br />
If you use a custom UI, you may need to download a special target window to implement the HoTT.
<br />

<br />
It is VERY useful seeing who is in the aggro list...also on raids it's fun to see a wizards name on the list before they...shall we say, blow up?  <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="Razz" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://home.comcast.net/~topknot/wsb/media/350795/site1015.jpg" border="0" />
